      "parameters": {
        "chatId": "7620524971",
        "text": "🚮 【訂單已永久刪除】\n📝 單號：{{ $('Receive Dashboard Order').first().json.body?.Order_ID || $('Receive Dashboard Order').first().json.Order_ID }}\n✅ 數據庫已完成清理。",
